description: Gets all the resource groups for a subscription.

filter.description: The filter to apply on the operation.You can filter by tag names and values. For example, to filter for a tag name and value, use $filter=tagName eq 'tag1' and tagValue eq 'Value1'

top.description: The number of results to return. If null is passed, returns all resource groups.

api_version.description: The API version to use for this operation.

subscription_id.description: The ID of the target subscription.
